7. Therefore, the definite integral from $a$ to $b$ is $[-2\cos(x/2 + 3)]_a^b = -2\cos(b/2 + 3) + 2\cos(a/2 + 3) = 2\cos(a/2 + 3) - 2\cos(b/2 + 3)$.

